## ðŸ› ï¸ Building From Source

### 1. Install Prerequisites
- Rust (latest stable)
- Node.js + pnpm
- Tauri dependencies:
  - Linux: apt install libsoup2.4-dev libwebkit2gtk-4.1-dev
  - macOS: Xcode tools
  - Windows: MSVC toolchain

### 2. Install JS deps
```bash
cd apps/desktop
pnpm install
```

### 3. Run Dev Mode
```bash
pnpm tauri dev
```

### 4. Build Release
```bash
pnpm tauri build
```
